ZH: 我们需要修建一个沟渠来排水。
EN: We need to build a ditch to drain the water.

ZH: 这个沟渠的设计非常巧妙。
EN: The design of this canal is very clever.

ZH: 农民们在田里挖了一个沟渠来灌溉农作物。
EN: The farmers dug a trench in the field to irrigate the crops.

ZH: 沟渠的两侧都种满了花草。
EN: Both sides of the canal are planted with flowers and plants.

ZH: 小溪从一个沟渠之中流出。
EN: The stream flows out from one of the ditches.

ZH: 我们需要疏通这个堵塞的沟渠。
EN: We need to dredge this blocked canal.

ZH: 沟渠的边缘有绿油油的草地。
EN: There is a lush green lawn along the edges of the ditch.

ZH: 这个村庄依靠沟渠的水源供应。
EN: This village relies on the water supply from the canals.

ZH: 在农田里修建了一个沟渠网络。
EN: A network of ditches was built in the farmland.

ZH: 这个沟渠需要经常清理，以免被杂物堵塞。
EN: This canal needs regular cleaning to prevent debris from clogging it.

ZH: 沟渠的水流缓慢而稳定。
EN: The water flow in the canal is slow and steady.

ZH: 这个沟渠起到了防洪的作用。
EN: This canal serves as a flood control measure.

ZH: 农民们将农作物种植在沟渠的旁边。
EN: Farmers grow crops next to the canal.

ZH: 这个沟渠连接了两个不同的水域。
EN: This canal connects two different bodies of water.

ZH: 沟渠的水很清澈，可以直接饮用。
EN: The water in the ditch is very clear and can be consumed directly.

ZH: 沟渠的河岸上有许多美丽的野花。
EN: There are many beautiful wildflowers on the canal banks.

ZH: 这个沟渠是由石头和水泥构建的。
EN: This canal is constructed with stones and cement.

ZH: 沟渠的一侧可以作为垂钓的好地方。
EN: One side of the ditch can be a good spot for fishing.

ZH: 沟渠旁边有一条小路通往村庄。
EN: There is a path leading to the village next to the ditch.

ZH: 这个沟渠是用来引导雨水流入排水系统的。
EN: This canal is used to divert rainwater into the drainage system.
